+#, php-format
+msgid "If you have multiple Phabricator environments (like a development/staging environment for working on testing Phabricator, and a production environment for deploying it), set the production environment URI here so that emails and other durable URIs will always generate with links pointing at the production environment. If unset, defaults to `%s`. Most installs do not need to set this option."
+msgstr ""
